Feature: User Authentication
Background:
	Given the user is going to register new account on Amazon Online Shopping
Scenario:
	Given the user is on user authentication Page
	And the user clicks the sign up button to go to sign up page
	When the user inputs the correct email address
	And the user creates the username
	And the user inputs the correct password
	And the user inputs the confirmation password
	And the user clicks the sign up button
	Then the user should be authenticated through email confirmation
	And the user redirected to their email
	And User clicks the confirmation link on the email
	And the user should be redirected to their Amazon Online Dashboard
	And the user should be presented with success message
